  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wavemaker Pacific 1 Pte. Ltd.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wavemaker Pacific 1 Pte. Ltd. (Wavemaker SEA Fund II or the Fund) is a $50 million early-stage VC fund focused on seed stage investments in the Southeast Asia region. The Fund aims to invest primarily in B2B companies led by exceptional entrepreneurs creating superior value by leveraging technology to deliver high-impact Automation, Data &amp; Intelligence. Wavemakers investment strategy is to build a large portfolio, exercise optionality, differentiate with stage (seed) and focus (B2B), and leverage its network.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">i.	Investment in sectors, business models and companies that support and nurture entrepreneurship, innovation, transparency, and access across the SEA region.
ii.	Provide access to capital to help grow nascent industry verticals of B2B and deep technology (AI, machine learning, 3D printing, virtual reality, etc.) in the SEA region.
iii.	Encourage operational, financial and E&amp;S improvements of local businesses.
iv.	Foster job creation and economic growth.</narrative>
  </description>
